Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Show me your face.\N-My face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"YUITO SUMERAGI SABOTAGED GOVERNMENT FACILITY"\N2nd Lieutenant Yuito Sumeragi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is now being hunted by the government
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for sabotaging a government facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We now move on to the next news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"JOURNEY TO TOGETSU"\NThat was too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"JOURNEY TO TOGETSU"\NFirst they put him on a pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they are treating him like a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was odd they made me into a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised to see you here, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since they branded me the traitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been worried you might\Nget caught up in trouble as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I discussed it with Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Should anything happen to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll escape to the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard anything from\NMajor General Fubuki since?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At the least, he managed to leave\Nthe old OSF hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't detect his tracks\Nfrom any system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the government didn't get to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Major General Fubuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For study purpose of our future plans\Nfor the Bell Peppers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's necessary to conduct a dissection\Nto extract the brain data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something from\Nthe hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taken to a different place\Nwhen we were captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That scientist said I was a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?\NYou can use your brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It could also be just a mistake on his end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't sit right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I am more concerned about our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Our priority is how to take the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no place for us here in Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I also think Seiran is just\Nas bad a place as Suoh for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, should we go to Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an autonomous religious region.\NThey are an independent city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We might obtain information\Neven those in Suoh and Seiran don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Karen mentioned it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what he meant by it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle once went to Togetsu\Nto close some business deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your uncle work for the OSF hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the business about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it involved the OSF hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's likely linked to the brain power experiment\Nand metamorphosis researches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Seiran had dealt with them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's safe to be in Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is indeed concerning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But since the hospital is involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we must go to Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing like my father and brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived this long without knowing\Nthe true nature of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still secrets I haven't uncovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I seek answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we have a slim chance\Nof finding a clue,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain's stance is firm.\NI'll follow your lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, we're headed for Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than waiting aimlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,why not search for a way to save Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it. Are you seriously going to Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned the routes of the trucks entering\Nthe facility where they keep Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They seemed to have come from Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no registration record,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but judging by the routes,\Nit's very likely they came from Togestsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ingredient used to make the ampoules
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was supplied by Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Madam Kyoka. That is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way Togetsu would be involved\Nin this massive operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You once told us you came from Togetsu\Nand were a preacher of the Togetsu Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are just a religious community\Nthat worships the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never known anyone\Nwho was involved in Other experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But Togetsu is a place with a long history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not surprising if they have information\Nthat we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding the research facility,\Nwe could ask Karen to save my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I thought that was the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But after contemplating the plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized there is much that we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.\NThey used human brains to conduct experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is Karen thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's keeping secrets from us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Suoh and Seiran forces' motives\Nare also questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasting our time siding with Karen\Nwho we can't trust
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a sound plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we go to Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we might find information\Nvital to save Naomi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, what is your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there is a chance to save my sister,\NI'll go to Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your horses, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard Karen back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was a slightest mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows what the people from Seiran\Nwould do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, it seems you don't want us in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would there be problems if we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Naomi will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen promised to keep\Nthat research facility safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't let Seiran meddle with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be sure about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me to monitor\Nthe Seiran forces and the research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll notify you if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. We'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find a way to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,KAITO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you to thank for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I was Alice's fiance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you are\Nthe OSF Major General of Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have use of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice joined the force\Non a sunny day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She was happy to have finally caught up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she had a kind heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubted if she could ever\Nbecome a proper soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She was clumsy and often sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You always said that about her.\NIt drove her mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was never truly upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought we would lose her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Had Alice retired peacefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless dwelling on the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.\NI'm in so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, please save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, we've deviated from the patrol route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't spotted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue to provide support from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. It's a relief to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our vehicle can't pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard the stories.\NBut this place is freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some places are covered in snow all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it only gets colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We might run into trouble\Nif there is a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up now, it's not too late\Nto have some hotpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to turn back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine your warm blanket and bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest with your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,my sweet Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's so...\N-Arashi, you're so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of you, enough with the chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not with those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers actually grow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi would be happy to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there are something weird here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Others are frequently found\Naround the snowfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still don't know where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the unsolved mystery\Nof the snowfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The coldness is enough to freeze any brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been walking for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How far are we from Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of city is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not exactly a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually a structure of the Togetsu Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The freaks there are obsessed with the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The place is pretty boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right to badmouth the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has the freedom of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on the faith itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the place has left you\Nwith no pleasant memory, Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might need some time\Nto understand the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand, you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, how is the weather in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The data show it's a sunny day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-An ice Other.\N-I've never seen one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This opened my eyes to\Nthe possibility of Other variants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An Ice Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The snowstorm stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the snowstorm was its doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they are the result\Nof desperate evolutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The OSF only told us the Others\Ncame from the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all we know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence gives me the creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I don't sense any human presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting the people from Togetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kasane, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kasane, you are our precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for the tardiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your "precious?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, do you understand what it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met the Togetsu Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a shame that you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lady Kasane, you were one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I came from Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kasane, you were born\Nwith powerful brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Himuka Government\Nwanted your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so they kidnapped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents were killed by Others\Nwhen I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Randall family took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the people of Togetsu have never
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten you, Lady Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your connection\Nwith the Other research facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We are obligated to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kasane, you are our only ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell my friends eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference to tell me right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We must resort to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We are outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have the brain\Nthat controls the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one is on his way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's even more isolated than the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Yuito is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Hanabi Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle has taken great care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I could say the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You welcome us despite our sudden visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be interested\Nin the knowledge we possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are our special guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You will probably find what you seek here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,THE MOON'S SECRETS
